Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,RO-OP2,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:23.49,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Com o peito coberto de lágrimas
Comment: 0,0:00:23.68,0:00:26.05,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Piso fundo no acelerador
Comment: 0,0:00:26.24,0:00:29.97,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Tentando esquecer aquela paixão
Comment: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:33.80,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Meu coração inquieto explode
Comment: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.36,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Naqueles dias, vivi sem freios
Comment: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:39.97,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,E agora o passado insiste em me alcançar
Comment: 0,0:00:41.25,0:00:42.22,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Ah, não...
Comment: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:49.40,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Sem olhar para trás, continuo correndo sem parar
Comment: 0,0:00:49.74,0:00:51.24,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Mas antes que eu percebesse
Comment: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:53.95,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Me perco novamente naquelas doces tentações
Comment: 0,0:00:54.79,0:00:57.05,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Liberte toda a sua força
Comment: 0,0:00:57.19,0:00:59.79,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,E seus desejos mais puros e intensos
Comment: 0,0:00:59.95,0:01:02.18,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Sou um pequeno fruto imaturo
Comment: 0,0:01:02.51,0:01:04.80,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Buscando, enfim, amadurecer
Comment: 0,0:01:04.97,0:01:07.34,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Vire sua coragem de ponta-cabeça
Comment: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:09.97,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Se a realidade não te satisfaz
Comment: 0,0:01:10.20,0:01:12.50,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Seus sentimentos não ganharão asas
Comment: 0,0:01:12.70,0:01:15.08,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Se não tiver o desejo de mudar
Comment: 0,0:01:17.91,0:01:20.30,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,De hoje em diante, viva o agora
Comment: 0,0:01:20.46,0:01:23.07,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,De amanhã em diante, construa o futuro
Comment: 0,0:01:23.07,0:01:27.98,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Vamos escrever uma nova história
Comment: 0,0:01:28.31,0:01:30.62,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Pode me emprestar só mais um pouco de força?
Comment: 0,0:01:30.74,0:01:33.40,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Não pare agora, cada luta te trouxe até aqui
Comment: 0,0:01:33.40,0:01:35.68,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Corte o vento com determinação
Comment: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:38.74,TR-OP2,,0,0,0,karaoke,E deixe seus sentimentos te guiarem
